OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK mortgage lending to fall
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin 2024 - trade body       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK lending for house purchases will    
OL,6, fall by 8% in 2024, a trade association
OL,7, representing banks is predicting.      
OL,9,FIn a report, UK Finance said higher    
OL,10,Finterest rates and household costs,    
OL,11,Fwill make it harder for people to      
OL,12,Faccess mortgage credit, which is based 
OL,13,Fon affordability.                      
OL,15,FIt predicts this trend will also lead  
OL,16,Fto falls across all lending next year, 
OL,17,Fand a higher number of repossessions.  
OL,19,FHowever, the outlook for lending is    
OL,20,Fexpected be brighter for 2025.         
